{"tid":1765301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"可以考慮下將港島大遊行變成分區大遊行","createTime":"2019-12-01T18:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T06:21:11.000Z","uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed8318d3610bc59e5cd1a57a64ea97c84c7035f","tid":1765301,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"例如屯天元、荃青、油尖旺、黃大仙、沙田大圍、上水粉嶺等等，地區相近作為遊行分區。<br />\n<br />\n1. 可以繼續鏡頭前聚人和理非<br />\n2. 有街坊支援物資同協助逃生<br />\n3. 分散狗力(尤其水車)，令佢地保守行動<br />\n4. 降低因交通封鎖而聚唔到人嘅機會<br />\n5. 唔食tg唔流眼淚，俾機會更多政治冷感港豬知道香港咩事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔熟各區地形，具體交俾大家探討下"},{"pid":"9955495a176037c3808341658b0295f6e042d9ac","tid":1765301,"uid":2607,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:08:06.000Z","msg":"訓撚左？8月5咩黎？<br />\n分花咩黎？"},{"pid":"e321c0c4e28dd8ae33c114631e7a04109797aa21","tid":1765301,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9955495a176037c3808341658b0295f6e042d9ac","tid":1765301,"uid":2607,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:08:06.000Z","msg":"訓撚左？8月5咩黎？<br />\n分花咩黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24822d09f7d3e33f4a2ff34cb57971184cc033ec","tid":1765301,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9955495a176037c3808341658b0295f6e042d9ac","tid":1765301,"uid":2607,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:08:06.000Z","msg":"訓撚左？8月5咩黎？<br />\n分花咩黎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:09:24.000Z","msg":"85罷工嚟喎"},{"pid":"118e2a6b208fcaf8b1a00dcd531a0ddc992bad4e","tid":1765301,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24822d09f7d3e33f4a2ff34cb57971184cc033ec","tid":1765301,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9955495a176037c3808341658b0295f6e042d9ac","tid":1765301,"uid":2607,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"cited